Package edu.cnm.deepdive.mealplanit.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Diet
    Model that creates the table in the database that allows accessors and mutators to change or access the information in the table.
    Person
    Model for creating the Person table in the database that allows accessors and mutators to access or change the the information in the table.
    PersonRestriction
    Model that holds the information for creating the PersonRestriction table in the database.
    Plan
    Model that holds the information for the Plan table when it is created in the database.
    PlanRestriction
    Model that holds the information for when the PlanRestriction table is created.
    Restriction
    A model for a table that holds Restriction modifiers in the database.
